{"id":102,"name":"التكاثر","transliteration":"At-Takathur","translation":"The Rivalry in world increase","type":"meccan","total_verses":8,"verses":[{"id":1,"text":"أَلۡهَىٰكُمُ ٱلتَّكَاثُرُ","translation":"Competition in [worldly] increase diverts you","transliteration":"Alhakumu alttakathuru"},{"id":2,"text":"حَتَّىٰ زُرۡتُمُ ٱلۡمَقَابِرَ","translation":"Until you visit the graveyards","transliteration":"Hatta zurtumu almaqabira"},{"id":3,"text":"كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"No! You are going to know","transliteration":"Kalla sawfa taAAlamoona"},{"id":4,"text":"ثُمَّ كَلَّا سَوۡفَ تَعۡلَمُونَ","translation":"Then no! You are going to know","transliteration":"Thumma kalla sawfa taAAlamoona"},{"id":5,"text":"كَلَّا لَوۡ تَعۡلَمُونَ عِلۡمَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"No! If you only knew with knowledge of certainty","transliteration":"Kalla law taAAlamoona AAilma alyaqeeni"},{"id":6,"text":"لَتَرَوُنَّ ٱلۡجَحِيمَ","translation":"You will surely see the Hellfire","transliteration":"Latarawunna aljaheema"},{"id":7,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتَرَوُنَّهَا عَيۡنَ ٱلۡيَقِينِ","translation":"Then you will surely see it with the eye of certainty","transliteration":"Thumma latarawunnaha AAayna alyaqeeni"},{"id":8,"text":"ثُمَّ لَتُسۡـَٔلُنَّ يَوۡمَئِذٍ عَنِ ٱلنَّعِيمِ","translation":"Then you will surely be asked that Day about pleasure","transliteration":"Thumma latusalunna yawmaithin AAani alnnaAAeemi"}]}
